lead_paragraph: Jets quarterback Bryce Petty threw a 44-yard touchdown pass to Robby Anderson before injuring his shoulder, but a pair of big plays helped the Philadelphia Eagles beat the New York Jets 14-6 Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Jets Quarterback Bryce Petty Injured in 14-6 Loss to Eagles
